    "repository": {
        "type": "git",

    "scripts": {
        "test": "npm run test-node && ([ -n \"${TRAVIS_PULL_REQUEST}\" -a \"${TRAVIS_PULL_REQUEST}\" != 'false' ] || npm run test-browser)",

        "test-browser-local": "zuul --local 8080 --no-coverage -- test/browser/*.js",
        "test-node": "tape test/node/*.js"
    },
    "version": "2.7.0",
    "bin": {}
